        "Title": "BCR VOL. 80 - Time Theft",
        "Location": "LOCATION_BANGKOK_ZIKA",
        "PublicId": "116081106883",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Bangkok/scene_zika.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 6098411b-1b38-45d8-b762-498a98f4bab2).Image",
        "Description": "47, \r\rour client is concerned with slimming the payroll margins of the staff at the Himmapan Hotel. They are concerned that Nabazov&apos;s event is overstaffed, and some employees present tonight are engaged in &quot;time theft&quot; - a real and preventable harm to corporate revenue and efficiency.\r\rIt&apos;s time for these slackers to drop their mops and clock out - permanently.\rI suggest you don&apos;t loaf around while you&apos;re fulfilling this contract.\rAnything less than your fastest time, may be time theft.\r\r-Loaf",
